== Overview ==

CATS is a FIJI plugin for context aware trainable segmentation of big image data. For more information please visit the GitHub [https://github.com/embl-cba/fiji-plugin-cats/blob/master/README.md#cats---context-aware-trainable-segmentation README].

== Installation ==

CATS can be installed from the ImageJ update site: http://sites.imagej.net/EMBL-CBA/. For details on how to install an update site click [[Following_an_update_site|here]].

To start CATS in ImageJ, select Plugins > Segmentation > CATS from the main menu.
